{
  "stem": "10283.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were all-- there were about 1,000 people on this ship, and most of them were Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were a few non-Jews and a few other passengers, but most of them were refugees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the crew was very respectful and very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no anti-Semitism or anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And like I said, I was 16.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had my first boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was very busy with all kinds of activities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was fine-- until we got to Havana.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took 10 days, at the time, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two weeks or 10 days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we got into Havana, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the police, the-- the immigration officers came on board.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they set themselves up in the dining room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We all filed in and showed our visas and our passports.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my parents went down to the cabin, and we packed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everything seemed to be going all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So then that night, they said, well, it's a slight delay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think you're going to stay overnight on board ship yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was hot and humid, and you know, May, and we weren't used to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We stayed most of night up on-- on-- on board, on deck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we weren't right in the harbor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were a little bit out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, the big-- And so they-- every day was something else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We stayed more or less a week, as I remember, in-- in Havana.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people were, of course, very desperate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because a lot of families were already separated, where the husband has already been there, and the wives were on the ship with children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so there were little boats coming from Havana and surrounding the Saint Louis.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
